					<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading mw-first-heading"><span class="mw-page-title-main">Kanawha County textbook controversy</span></h1>
				
							
<div id="p-lang-btn" class="vector-menu vector-dropdown vector-menu-dropdown mw-portlet mw-portlet-lang"  >
